          "effect": "The artist flings ink in the attacker's eyes. The attacker must succeed at a DC 18 Reflex save or be blinded. This takes effect before the attacker targets the artist. The blindness lasts until the end of the target's next turn, but the creature can Interact to rub its eyes to attempt a new save to end the condition.",
